<OUTPUT_TEXT>
• Answer all incoming calls promptly and professionally
• Greet callers courteously and identify the practice/department
• Determine nature of call and caller's needs
• Transfer calls to appropriate staff member or department
• Take detailed messages when staff are unavailable
• Manage multiple phone lines as needed
• Handle patient inquiries and route clinical questions to medical staff
• Maintain up-to-date staff directory and extensions
• Follow HIPAA guidelines to protect patient privacy
• Document all calls in the phone log system
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
